title: South Park The Fractured But Whole - CODEPUNKS, Update
description:
About the game:
South Park: The Fractured but Whole is a role-playing video game.
The Fractured but Whole takes place after the events of South Park: The Stick of Truth, with the 21st season episode Franchise Prequel as a tie-in.
The children begin a new adventure, again set in the town of South Park in the Colorado Rocky Mountains, this time becoming role-playing superheroes.
However, a falling-out over Cartman's planned film franchise splinters the boys into two groups.

INSTALLATION:
1.Install and choose your options
2.Copy Crack from CODEPUNKS dir to installdir
if you didnt choose to copy the crack automatically
3.That's it, Enjoy the Game
